This project is inspired by and builds upon ideas from several open-source projects:

### Solhint
- License: MIT
- Copyright (c) 2017 Protofire
- URL: https://github.com/protofire/solhint
- Usage: Architecture patterns and lint rule concepts

### Slither
- License: AGPLv3
- Copyright (c) 2018 Trail of Bits
- URL: https://github.com/crytic/slither
- Usage: Security analysis concepts and vulnerability detection patterns
- Important Note: This project implements security detectors inspired by Slither's
  concepts but does not directly copy or port AGPLv3-licensed code. All security
  detection logic is independently implemented under MIT license. If you wish to
  incorporate actual Slither code or detectors, you must comply with AGPLv3 terms.

### Tlin
- License: MIT
- Copyright (c) 2024 Gnoland
- URL: https://github.com/gnolang/tlin
- Usage: CLI architecture and parallel processing patterns

### Solidity Parser
- License: MIT
